Package org.hms.services.medicalrecord

Class MedicalRecordService

java.lang.Object
org.hms.services.AbstractService<IMedicalDataInterface>
org.hms.services.medicalrecord.MedicalRecordService
public class MedicalRecordService extends AbstractService<IMedicalDataInterface>
MedicalRecordService is responsible for managing medical records, personal particulars, and contact information related to patients in the system. It extends the AbstractService class and implements methods for handling various operations such as retrieving medical records, updating patient information, and managing medical entries by doctors.

      patientID - The unique identifier of the patient for whom the medical entry is being added.

      true if the medical entry was successfully added, false otherwise.
